MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-69. Moore v. Dayton Power & Light Co. Montgomery County, No. 14482.

This cause is pending before the court on the certification of conflict by the Court of Appeals for Montgomery County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, effective April 20,1995, that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed. ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
